01:11:09,666 --> 01:11:11,291
No one will call you Pooja's husband.

1526
01:11:11,375 --> 01:11:14,166
Listen, you idiot. Get lost.

1527
01:11:14,250 --> 01:11:15,500
Uncle, who is Pooja?

1528
01:11:15,583 --> 01:11:17,916
