-Get out.

1532
01:11:26,041 --> 01:11:27,125
Get lost.

1533
01:11:28,041 --> 01:11:29,875
-Have some.
-It's okay.

1534
01:11:31,166 --> 01:11:36,875
Look, as soon as
you fulfill all my conditions,

1535
01:11:37,083 --> 01:11:40,083
only then will we start preparing
for the wedding.

1536
01:11:40,208 --> 01:11:43,583
